==Usage==
To use the template, start with {{tlc|CJKV}} and add any parameters you like, along with what you want to be displayed. The template will display all and only, the parameters that you give it. The following parameters are supported:
;Parameters
{|class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description !! Example
|-
| {{para|t}} || [[:en:Traditional Chinese characters|traditional Chinese]] || {{tlx|CJKV|t{{=}}李四}}<br />{{CJKV|t=李四}}
|-
| {{para|s}} || [[:en:Simplified Chinese characters|simplified Chinese]] || {{tlx|CJKV|s{{=}}李四}}<br />{{CJKV|s=李四}}
|-
| {{para|c}} || [[:en:Chinese language|Chinese]] || {{tlx|CJKV|c{{=}}李四}}<br />{{CJKV|c=李四}}
|-
| {{para|p}} || [[:en:Pinyin|Hanyu Pinyin]] || {{tlx|CJKV|p{{=}}Zhōnghuá Mínguó}}<br />{{CJKV|p=Zhōnghuá Mínguó}}
|-
| {{para|tp}} || [[:en:Tongyong Pinyin|Tongyong Pinyin]] || {{tlx|CJKV|tp{{=}}Jhonghuá Mínguó}}<br />{{CJKV|tp=Jhonghuá Mínguó}}
|-
| {{para|cy}} || [[:en:Cantonese Yale|Cantonese Yale]] || {{tlx|CJKV|cy{{=}}lei5 sei3}}<br />{{CJKV|cy=lei5 sei3}}
|-
| {{para|cj}} || [[:en:Jyutping|Cantonese Jyutping]] || {{tlx|CJKV|cj{{=}}lei5 sei3}}<br />{{CJKV|cj=lei5 sei3}}
|-
| {{para|w}} || [[:en:Wade–Giles|Wade–Giles]] || {{tlx|CJKV|w{{=}}Chung-hua Min-kuo}}<br />{{CJKV|w=Chung-hua Min-kuo}}
|-
| {{para|j}} || [[:en:Japanese language|Japanese]] || {{tlx|CJKV|j{{=}}中華人民共和国}}<br />{{CJKV|j=中華人民共和国}}
|-
| {{para|r}} || [[:en:Romanization of Japanese|Rōmaji]] || {{tlx|CJKV|r{{=}}Chūka jinmin kyōwa-koku}}<br />{{CJKV|r=Chūka jinmin kyōwa-koku}}
|-
| {{para|k}} || [[:en:Korean language|Korean]] || {{tlx|CJKV|k{{=}}중화 인민 공화국}}<br />{{CJKV|k=중화 인민 공화국}}
|-
| {{para|rr}} || [[Romanization of Korean|Romaja]] || {{tlx|CJKV|rr{{=}}Junghwa inmin gonghwaguk}}<br />{{CJKV|rr=Junghwa inmin gonghwaguk}}
|-
| {{para|v}} || [[:en:Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]] || {{tlx|CJKV|v{{=}}Trung Quốc}}<br />{{CJKV|v=Trung Quốc}}
|-
| {{para|l}} || [[:en:en:Literal translation|en:Literal translation]] || {{tlx|CJKV|l{{=}}China}}<br />{{CJKV|l=China}}
|-
|}
''(Note: "Japanese pronunciation" or "Korean pronunciation" will appear, instead of "rōmaji" or "romaja", if their Japanese and Korean parameters are missing respectively. See examples 6 and 7.)''

All parameters are optional.

==Examples==
Traditional Chinese always goes first.
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=張三|s=张三}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=張三|s=张三}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|s=张三|t=張三}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|s=张三|t=張三}}

This template compares traditional Chinese, simplified Chinese and Japanese Kanji automatically.
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=李四}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=李四}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|s=李四}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|s=李四}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四|j=李四}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四|j=李四}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四|j=李四|k=이사}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四|j=李四|k=이사}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四|j=李四|k=이사|l=foobar}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=李四|s=李四|j=李四|k=이사|l=foobar}}

Simplified and traditional Chinese can be combined together.
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=皇居|s=皇居|j=皇居|k=고쿄}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=皇居|s=皇居|j=皇居|k=고쿄}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|c=皇居|j=皇居|k=고쿄}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|c=皇居|j=皇居|k=고쿄}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|c=皇居|j=皇居|k=고쿄|l=Imperial Residence}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|c=皇居|j=皇居|k=고쿄|l=Imperial Residence}}

Note that the combined Chinese parameter will overwrite existing ones.
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=黃飛鴻|s=黄飞鸿|c=黄飞鸿|j=黄飛鴻|k=황비홍}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=黃飛鴻|s=黄飞鸿|c=黄飞鸿|j=黄飛鴻|k=황비홍}}<br />is equivalent to
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|c=黄飞鸿|j=黄飛鴻|k=황비홍}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|c=黄飞鸿|j=黄飛鴻|k=황비홍}}

More examples:
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=中國|s=中国|j=中國|k=중국}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=中國|s=中国|j=中國|k=중국}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=中國|s=中国|j=中国|k=중국}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=中國|s=中国|j=中国|k=중국}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|c=立春|j=立春|k=입춘|v=Lập xuân|l=establishment of spring}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|c=立春|j=立春|k=입춘|v=Lập xuân|l=establishment of spring}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=漢族|s=汉族|p=hànzú|j=漢民族|r=kan minzoku|k=한족}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=漢族|s=汉族|p=hànzú|j=漢民族|r=kan minzoku|k=한족}}
# <code><nowiki>{{CJKV|t=中華民國|s=中华民国|p=Zhōnghuá Mínguó|tp=Jhonghuá Mínguó|w=Chung-hua Min-kuo}}</nowiki></code><br />{{CJKV|t=中華民國|s=中华民国|p=Zhōnghuá Mínguó|tp=Jhonghuá Mínguó|w=Chung-hua Min-kuo}}
# <code><nowiki>'''Emperor''' ({{CJKV|c=皇帝|p=Huángdì|r=Kōtei|rr=Hwangje|v=Hoàng đế}})</nowiki></code><br />'''Emperor''' ({{CJKV|c=皇帝|p=Huángdì|r=Kōtei|rr=Hwangje|v=Hoàng đế}})
# <code><nowiki>'''History of China''' ({{CJKV|t=中國歷史|s=中国历史|p=Zhōngguó lìshǐ|j=中国の歴史|r=Chūgoku no rekishi|k=중국의 역사|rr=Junggugui Yeoksa|v=Lịch sử Trung Quốc}})</nowiki></code><br />'''History of China''' ({{CJKV|t=中國歷史|s=中国历史|p=Zhōngguó lìshǐ|j=中国の歴史|r=Chūgoku no rekishi|k=중국의 역사|rr=Junggugui Yeoksa|v=Lịch sử Trung Quốc}})

==See also==
*{{tlx|Infobox Chinese}} – infobox template supports traditional, simplified Chinese as well as other common romanizations.

